                </p>

                <p>
                    基于共同的使命、愿景、价值观以及管理理念，逐步建立起特色的企业文化，作为我们发展的基石，目前服务的客户已经覆盖全国各地以及数十个行业，目前正处在蓬勃发展壮大当中。
                    路人甲总部在广州，在坚持核心价值观的前提下，十分注重员工个人与公司共同成长。对新员工，根据不同条件安排不同的培训计划，重点培养员工的学习能力与团队协作能力。对于资深员工，重在培养带领新人和项目产品把控，以老带新，传道授业解惑的导师制。
                    产品服务方面，路人甲软件以“通过技术与服务，优质人们的生活”为使命，注重细节，追求完美，不断突破自我，为客户提供具有良好用户体验的产品与服务。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xs-12">
                <p>
                    Lunjar is an advanced domestic internet application service provider. </p>
                <p>
                    According to the common mission, vision, values and the concept of management, we have set up our attractive and competitive civilization of company, which becomes our foundation and motivation in the future development. Currently, customers using our service cover the whole country and spread widely . our company is located in Guangzhou. Staff's progress related to the company's improvement is based on the premise of core value perception. For a new staff, we will arrange different training plans for newers on their personalities, and the key of training is the educational ability and cooperation. While for a senior, the main responsibility is item controlling, as well being the leader for new staff who passes experience to the next generation. In the field of production service, Lunar takes "being a better life via technology and service" as the mission. Details must be considered and production must be creative. Providing excellent production and service for clients motivates us pursuing perfection.

